---
/*
  VOICE REFERENCES:
  
  PROPHET: "Put on the armor of YAHUAH. The enemy prowls—but you have authority."
  OG MENTOR: "Discipline beats drama. Obedience defeats the enemy. Period."
  HOOD PHILOSOPHER: "You fight like you train. So train like your life depends on it—because it does."
  ENTREPRENEUR: "Spiritual warfare isn't expense; it's investment in victory."
  
  SACRED NAMES: YAHUAH, YAHUSHA, RUACH HAQODESH, EL ELYON
*/
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Spiritual Warfare">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 md:py-16 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-amber-100">Spiritual Warfare</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-amber-900/30 border-2 border-amber-600 rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8 my-8 not-prose">
        <p class="text-amber-100 text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-0">
          Discipline beats drama. Obedience defeats the enemy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="lead text-xl text-neutral-300">
        We do not wrestle against flesh and blood, but against principalities, powers, rulers of darkness, 
        and spiritual wickedness in high places (Ephesians 6:12).
      </p>

      <h2>The Armor of YAHUAH</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300">
        Put on the full armor daily. This is not symbolic—it's your spiritual covering:
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-3 not-prose">
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="text-amber-100 font-bold mb-1">Belt of Truth</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Stand firm in the Word of YAHUAH. Lies cannot penetrate truth.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="text-amber-100 font-bold mb-1">Breastplate of Righteousness</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Walk in holiness. Guard your heart from compromise.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="text-amber-100 font-bold mb-1">Shoes of the Gospel of Peace</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Be ready to share the Good News. Move in His authority.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="text-amber-100 font-bold mb-1">Shield of Faith</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Quench every fiery dart of the enemy with unwavering trust in YAHUAH.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="text-amber-100 font-bold mb-1">Helmet of Salvation</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Guard your mind. Know your position in YAHUSHA is secure.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="text-amber-100 font-bold mb-1">Sword of the Spirit</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Wield the Word of YAHUAH. It's your offensive weapon—sharp and living.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Close the Doorways</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300">
        The enemy gains access through open doors: unrepented sin, unforgiveness, trauma, occult involvement, 
        generational curses, and ungodly soul ties. Identify them. Confess them. Close them in YAHUSHA's Name.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
        <h3 class="text-amber-100 font-bold mb-3">Common Doorways</h3>
        <ul class="text-neutral-400 space-y-2 mb-0 text-sm">
          <li>Sexual immorality and pornography</li>
          <li>Unforgiveness and bitterness</li>
          <li>Occult practices (tarot, astrology, witchcraft)</li>
          <li>Trauma and unhealed wounds</li>
          <li>Generational sin passed down through bloodlines</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p class="text-neutral-300">
        Use the <a href="/prayer-and-fasting" class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 underline">micro-liturgy for closing doorways</a> to shut these access points. 
        Then stand guard. Don't reopen what YAHUAH has sealed.
      </p>

      <h2>Authority in YAHUSHA</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300">
        You have been given authority to trample on serpents and scorpions and over all the power of the enemy (Luke 10:19). 
        Use the Name of YAHUSHA. Resist the devil, and he will flee (James 4:7).
      </p>

      <!-- Next Steps -->
      <div class="mt-12 bg-neutral-950 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-100 mb-6 text-center">Continue Your Training</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <a href="/prayer-and-fasting" class="group block p-6 bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 hover:border-amber-700 transition-colors">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-100 group-hover:text-amber-200 mb-2">Prayer & Fasting</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Use the micro-liturgy to close spiritual doorways</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/identity-and-messiah" class="group block p-6 bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 hover:border-amber-700 transition-colors">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-100 group-hover:text-amber-200 mb-2">Identity & Mashiach</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Know your authority in YAHUSHA HAMASHIACH</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/end-times" class="group block p-6 bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 hover:border-amber-700 transition-colors">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-100 group-hover:text-amber-200 mb-2">End-Times</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Prepare for the final battle and YAHUSHA's return</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
